Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: JSON parsing errors when loading configuration files

Solution: Validate JSON syntax using python3 -m json.tool config/program_config.json
Check for missing commas, brackets, or quotes
Issue: Date calculation errors in timeline generation

Solution: Ensure date format is consistent (YYYY-MM-DD)
Use datetime.strptime() with correct format string
Handle timezone considerations if needed
Issue: Empty or missing reports

Solution: Verify all prerequisite files exist before running dependent scripts
Check file paths are relative to script execution directory
Ensure directories exist before writing files
Issue: Metrics simulation produces unrealistic values

Solution: Adjust random number ranges to match realistic scenarios
Consider using normal distribution instead of uniform random
Add validation to ensure metrics stay within logical bounds
Conclusion
This lab demonstrated the complete lifecycle of executing long-term security programs. You learned to:

Design multi-year security strategies with measurable objectives
Create detailed project plans with phases, tasks, and milestones
Implement automated monitoring systems for continuous program assessment
